parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select
count(dates.ymd) as Total_Days_avai
from listings l 
left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id = l.id 
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2022-12-16', timestamp '2023-01-02', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
where ll.country = 'Malaysia'

SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select
A.rej_booking,
A.fuld_booking,
A.fuld_listings,
ROUND(((A.fuld_booking::numeric/nullif(A.spec_req,0))*100),2) as AFR_rate,
A.GMV
from
(select
count(distinct case when ((b.status in ('accepted', 'completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection','return_car')) or (b.status in ('withdrawn','cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') or (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null))) then b.id end) as spec_req,
count(distinct case when b.status in ('accepted', 'completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection','return_car') then b.id end) as fuld_booking,
count(distinct case when b.status in ('accepted', 'completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection','return_car') then b.listing_id end) as fuld_listings,
count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.id end) as rej_booking,
sum(case when b.status in ('accepted', 'waiting_for_inspection', 'start_driving', 'return_car', 'completed') 
then (case when d3.del_pickup_disc is null and d4.del_dropoff_disc is null then b.gross_amount 
else b.gross_amount + coalesce(d1.del_pickup, 0) + coalesce(d2.del_dropoff, 0)
- coalesce(d3.del_pickup_disc, 0) - coalesce(d4.del_dropoff_disc, 0) end) end) as GMV
from bookings b 
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
left join
(select bl.booking_id, bl.amount as del_pickup from booking_lines bl where bl.slug = 'car-pick-up-fee') d1
on b.id = d1.booking_id
left join
(select bl.booking_id, bl.amount as del_dropoff from booking_lines bl where bl.slug = 'car-drop-off-fee') d2
on b.id = d2.booking_id
left join
(select bl.booking_id, bl.amount as del_pickup_disc from booking_lines bl where bl.slug = 'car-pick-up-discount-fee') d3
on b.id = d3.booking_id
left join
(select bl.booking_id, bl.amount as del_dropoff_disc from booking_lines bl where bl.slug = 'car-drop-off-discount-fee') d4
on b.id = d4.booking_id
where b.request_end_at >= '2022-12-16 00:00' and b.request_start_at <= '2023-01-02 23:59'
and ll.country = 'Malaysia')A

parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no, 
m.name as model,
case when ll.city_id in (1) then '1. KV'   
when ll.city_id in (2,12) then '2. PG'
when ll.city_id in (3,19,20,21) then '3. KK'  
when ll.city_id in (4,15) then '4. JB' 
when ll.city_id in (5) then '5. IP' 
when ll.city_id in (47) then '6. NS'
when ll.city_id in (13) then '7. LGK'
else '8. Others' end as city,
l.user_id, 
concat(u.first_name, ' ',u.last_name)as host_name, 
u.email, 
u.phone_number,
case when bj.rej_booking is null then '0' else bj.rej_booking end as rej_booking,
la.avai_days,
case when bc.fuld_booking is null then '0' else bc.fuld_booking end as fuld_booking,
case when fd.fuld_days is null then '0' else fd.fuld_days end as fuld_days
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) as rej_booking
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at >= '2022-12-16 00:00' and b.request_start_at <= '2023-01-02 23:59'
        group by 1)bj
        on bj.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted') then b.id end) as fuld_booking
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at >= '2022-12-16 00:00' and b.request_start_at <= '2023-01-02 23:59'
        group by 1)bc
        on bc.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select l.id,
        count(dates.ymd) as avai_days
        from listings l
        left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id=l.id
        left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2022-12-16', timestamp '2023-01-02', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
        dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
        where l.status='approved' and l.deleted_at is null 
        GROUP BY 1)la
        on la.id = l.id
--
left join
                (select distinct b.listing_id,
                count(distinct dates.ymd) as fuld_days
                from bookings b 
                left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id 
                join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2022-12-16', '2023-01-02' , interval '1 day')::date as ymd) dates 
                on dates.ymd between b.request_start_at::date and b.request_end_at::date
                where b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted')
                and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
                group by 1)fd
                on fd.listing_id = l.id
where l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
